  ('Trends','129580','Eon Spinner Pen','eon-spinner-pen-129580','Pens','Novelty Pens','A retractable recycled aluminium ballpoint pen combining everyday writing performance with an integrated fidget spinner ring. The smooth spinning action of the recycled aluminium ring adds a fun and tactile element during use, while the matte finish barrel with shiny chrome trim delivers a modern, refined appearance. It is fitted with a Parker-style refill containing 1800m of black Dokumental ink, providing long-lasting and consistent writing performance. An optional pen sleeve is available at additional cost.','Personalise the the Eon Spinner Pen with pad print per colour/position or screen print — a retractable recycled aluminium ballpoint pen combining everyday writing performance with an integrated fidget spinner ring. From 250 units.',250,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "Gunmetal", "hex": "#2A3439", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-3.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-4.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "#F5D400", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-5.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "#F26722", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-6.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-7.webp"}, {"name": "Forest Green", "hex": "#1B5E20", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-8.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "#7DD3FC", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129580-9.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "