  ('Trends','129665','Corsica Coffee Cup','corsica-coffee-cup-129665','Drinkware','Coffee Cups','The Corsica Coffee Cup is a 350ml double wall coffee cup with a clean, modern profile designed for everyday use. It features a sturdy stainless steel outer with a polypropylene inner, providing durability alongside practical insulation. The flip closure lid folds all the way back for easy drinking while the smooth, painted finish is available in a range of great colours to suit your brand. The colour match lid and cup completes the look for a consistent, considered appearance. Presented in a natural gift box.','Add your logo to the Corsica Coffee Cup with pad print per colour/position or screen print — the Corsica Coffee Cup is a 350ml double wall coffee cup with a clean, modern profile designed for everyday use. From 25 units.',25,true,null,'supplier',null,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-2.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "#F5D400", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-3.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "#F26722", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-4.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "#E85D9E", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-5.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-6.webp"}, {"name": "Bright Green", "hex": "#66BB2E", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-7.webp"}, {"name": "Dark Green", "hex": "#14532D", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/trends/products/_variants/w400/129665-8.webp"}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "#008C