  ('Trends','129721','Sonny Custom Bucket Hat with Full Colour Patch','sonny-custom-bucket-hat-with-full-colour-patch-129721','Headwear','Bucket Hats','A fully customisable polyester bucket hat lined with poplin material for comfort and structure. It features edge-to-edge full colour print and a full colour sublimation patch available in three shape options for high impact branding. Available in three sizes to fit most people, including kids, making it a versatile fit across a wide audience. The fabric complies with AS/NZS standards for sun protection. A production lead time of 35 working days applies via air freight','Brand the the Sonny Custom Bucket Hat with Full Colour Patch with full colour patch or sublimation print — a fully customisable polyester bucket hat lined with poplin material for comfort and structure. From 100 units.',100,true,null,'supplier',null,null,'indent_air',null);
