  ('Trends','133391','Custom Mens Active Tank Top','custom-mens-active-tank-top-133391','Apparel','Teamwear','A fully customisable men''s tank top made from a breathable 180gsm 100% polyester mesh fabric and designed for lightweight comfort and active wear. It features a regular fit with bias finished armholes and collar for added durability and a clean look. Edge-to-edge full colour sublimation print delivers bold, high impact branding across the entire garment, perfect for teamwear, sporting clubs and events. A production lead time of 30 working days applies via air freight.','Add your logo to the Custom Mens Active Tank Top with sublimation print — a fully customisable men''s tank top made from a breathable 180gsm 100% polyester mesh fabric and designed for lightweight comfort and active wear. From 10 units.',10,true,null,'supplier','{"sizes": ["XS", "S", "M", "L", "XL", "2XL", "3XL", "4XL", "5XL"], "rows": [{"label": "Half Chest cm", "values": ["41", "45", "49", "53", "57", "61", "56", "69", "73"]}, {"label": "Length cm", "values": ["61.5", "64.5", "67.5", "70.5", "73.5", "75", "76.5", "78", "79.5"]}]}'::jsonb,null,'indent_air',null);
