  ('Trends','133394','Custom Mens Active T-Shirt','custom-mens-active-t-shirt-133394','Apparel','T-Shirts','A fully customisable men''s active t-shirt made from breathable 180gsm 100% polyester mesh fabric, designed for lightweight comfort and active wear. It features a regular fit with a crew neck and raglan sleeves for ease of movement and a modern athletic look. Edge-to-edge full colour sublimation print delivers bold, high impact branding across the entire garment, perfect for teamwear, sporting clubs and events. A production lead time of 30 working days applies via air freight.','Put your logo on the Custom Mens Active T-Shirt with sublimation print — a fully customisable men''s active t-shirt made from breathable 180gsm 100% polyester mesh fabric, designed for lightweight comfort and active wear. From 10 units.',10,true,null,'supplier','{"sizes": ["XS", "S", "M", "L", "XL", "2XL", "3XL", "4XL", "5XL"], "rows": [{"label": "Half Chest cm", "values": ["44", "48", "52", "56", "60", "64", "68", "72", "76"]}, {"label": "Length cm", "values": ["68", "71", "74", "77", "80", "81.5", "83", "84.5", "86"]}]}'::jsonb,null,'indent_air',null);
